競技性の高い5v5のMOBAアクションゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: チャンピオンを選ぼう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Reworked and retrofitted for gaming on the go, League of Legends: Wild Rift brings the franchise’s twitchy thrills, unmatched depth, and nail-biting tactics to iPhone and iPad. Each match is a fast-paced 5v5 tug-of-war. Pick from dozens of champions and head onto the battlefield, charging down one of three lanes as you help your team destroy the enemy’s Nexus. Combining slick, accessible touchscreen controls with the tactical brilliance that turned League of Legends into a worldwide sensation, Wild Rift is a must-play MOBA for newcomers and vets alike.
